    "name": "Jin & Jan",
    "steam_appid": 3024110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/b68ba858f87b549f7cbf6bfbd5efe6bd.avif?t=1743699723\" width=618 height=91 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《阴与阳》 反向双控鬼魅可爱的益智游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阴和阳, 在一次恶作剧中将世界一分为二： 光明和黑暗。现在，这对无畏的幽灵兄弟必须在这场集益智和技巧于一体的刺激冒险中恢复世界的平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 阳会听从你的指挥，但他的哥哥扬却总是朝相反的方向移动。你必须仔细把握每一步的时间，因为敌人会对你的动作做出反应：有些会实时移动，有些则会与阳同步移动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阴和阳将带你闯过难度越来越高的关卡，在这些关卡中，你将输掉比赛，并研究如何战胜这些关卡。每克服一个挑战，你就离掌握这对奇特的兄弟更近了一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/7211b8c77e7cb4b496556a513626d026.avif?t=1743699723\" width=618 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魂系类益智游戏</strong>：通过需要协调和战略思维的谜题考验你的技巧。死亡也是旅程的一部分。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/650d8dec741c42bee4307611ce08d5cf.poster.avif?t=1743699723\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/650d8dec741c42bee4307611ce08d5cf.webm?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/650d8dec741c42bee4307611ce08d5cf.mp4?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌人和障碍:</strong> 面对各种敌人和障碍，考验你的技巧。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/ef1bb287a3eab39737b68550df66d8a8.poster.avif?t=1743699723\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/ef1bb287a3eab39737b68550df66d8a8.webm?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/ef1bb287a3eab39737b68550df66d8a8.mp4?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满挑战的关卡</strong>: 45 个关卡等着考验你的智慧 。 你能全部完成吗？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/9883b50e5984eac231393d2413b3bd7c.poster.avif?t=1743699723\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/9883b50e5984eac231393d2413b3bd7c.webm?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/9883b50e5984eac231393d2413b3bd7c.mp4?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>老少皆宜：</strong>《阴与阳》是一款老少皆宜的游戏，非常适合独自玩耍或与朋友和家人一起玩。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/5cb7303b4fe6a50823f49c5a9ec6d6ae.poster.avif?t=1743699723\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/5cb7303b4fe6a50823f49c5a9ec6d6ae.webm?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/5cb7303b4fe6a50823f49c5a9ec6d6ae.mp4?t=1743699723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024110/extras/7cf32df22b77faef4094282287c1b357.avif?t=1743699723\" width=618 height=115 /></span></p>",
